## Scripts Úteis

### PHP (Composer)

```bash
# Rodar todos os testes
composer test

# Rodar testes com coverage
composer test:coverage

# Corrigir código (Laravel Pint)
composer code:fix

# Verificar código sem modificar
composer code:check

# Rodar QA completo (verificação + testes)
composer qa

# Limpar todos os caches
composer clear-all
```

### JavaScript (NPM)

```bash
